Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.20,0:21:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,02 收到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.95,0:21:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…自衛隊會在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.30,0:21:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,累死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.65,0:21:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們還活著吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.40,0:21:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.20,0:21:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹掉牠了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.25,0:21:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.90,0:21:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我終於報仇了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.65,0:21:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那妳以後就別再叫我爸爸了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.35,0:21:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要　因為人家已經叫習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.05,0:21:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
